Town & Country to close distribution unit . Town & Country Corp . , a maker of fine jewelry , said Tuesday it will close its Dallas distribution facility as part of its restructuring to cut costs . The company said it will transfer the operations to its headquarters in Chelsea , Mass . , during the next two months , creating 45 jobs there . The Dallas sales force will remain in Texas , it said . Town & Country also has manufacturing facilities in New York , Hong Kong and Bangkok , Thailand and has 1 , 300 employees worldwide . Town & Country ' s stock edged up 6 . 25 cents to 37 . 5 cents on the American Stock Exchange . 
